headline: Georgia Power restores power to 230,000+ customers following Winter Storm Cora
summary: Crews navigating icy roads, wind and continuing winter weather in restoration efforts;Company expects to restore power to nearly all impacted customers Saturday ATLANTA, Jan. 11, 2025...
